com.nutiteq.components
Class MutableMapPos

java.lang.Object
  com.nutiteq.components.MutableMapPos

public class MutableMapPos
extends java.lang.Object

Map position defined using three coordinates. X and y coordinates denote positions on the map, while z coordinate is height from the ground plane. Actual units for x, y and z depend on map projection. For example, in EPSG:4326 x is used for latitude and y is used for longitude. This is mutable version of MapPos class.
